         VERSION=8.0.1
     SOURCE_HASH=sha512:e1292f059b07a5aa2f3fbf345b893209cac895c461b4abf30b8b76bcd03c79dd09f911450293403070e1a0bb08496a7f37693ba5a62a9d423dd6ba55e744444d
